1
00:00:18,018 --> 00:00:19,686
I'm... sorry

2
00:00:23,189 --> 00:00:23,982
For what?

3
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:28,028
Just...

4
00:00:28,653 --> 00:00:30,280
For putting us in this situation

5
00:00:33,324 --> 00:00:34,868
Nah

6
00:00:35,118 --> 00:00:36,411
It's not like you forced me

7
00:00:37,662 --> 00:00:38,830
And...

8
00:00:39,706 --> 00:00:40,832
I liked it too

9
00:00:44,794 --> 00:00:46,838
Me too

10
00:00:49,215 --> 00:00:50,467
Lucifer...

11
00:00:52,427 --> 00:00:54,137
Why did you come here?

12
00:00:54,929 --> 00:00:57,182
Were you really here to drink human blood?

13
00:01:02,353 --> 00:01:03,271
Do you really see me

14
00:01:03,271 --> 00:01:04,856
as nothing but a villain?

15
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:09,152
I didn't mean that

16
00:01:15,992 --> 00:01:16,868
Then?

17
00:01:22,749 --> 00:01:24,834
You bit my neck,

18
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:26,836
so that's proof

19
00:01:39,849 --> 00:01:40,850
Honestly...

20
00:01:42,685 --> 00:01:45,063
I don't know why I bit you either

21
00:01:48,274 --> 00:01:50,068
I wasn't in my right mind back then

22
00:01:51,778 --> 00:01:53,113
The scent of your blood...

23
00:01:55,281 --> 00:01:57,283
It felt like it would save me

24
00:02:01,287 --> 00:02:02,831
Save you?

25
00:02:04,582 --> 00:02:05,875
Come to think of it...

26
00:02:06,167 --> 00:02:07,335
that scar on your arm

27
00:02:10,505 --> 00:02:12,841
Family

28
00:02:14,592 --> 00:02:17,303
It's a word that both saves me and destroys me

29
00:02:18,388 --> 00:02:19,472
Family

30
00:02:23,977 --> 00:02:26,479
My father broke the rules of the vampires

31
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:29,566
and fell in love with a human woman

32
00:02:31,818 --> 00:02:34,154
And I'm what came from the two of them

33
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,867
My grandfather said

34
00:02:38,867 --> 00:02:41,911
he couldn't accept a human woman
as his daughter-in-law

35
00:02:42,662 --> 00:02:44,831
so he cast my mother out

36
00:02:46,332 --> 00:02:49,169
I longed to see my mother's face but never could

37
00:02:51,337 --> 00:02:53,506
I just wanted to see it at least once

38
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,845
I see

39
00:03:01,514 --> 00:03:02,849
And my brother...

40
00:03:03,057 --> 00:03:04,559
He got afraid I'd get in the way of his succession

41
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:06,853
So he always wanted me dead

42
00:03:08,521 --> 00:03:10,857
But since I can't die in the vampire world,

43
00:03:12,275 --> 00:03:14,319
he kept hunting me down

44
00:03:16,738 --> 00:03:18,865
That's how I got this scar on my arm

45
00:03:21,576 --> 00:03:22,827
Wow...

46
00:03:24,245 --> 00:03:25,663
That must have had it so hard

47
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:30,835
But somehow...

48
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:34,839
when I look at you,
I feel like I'm looking at myself

49
00:03:42,847 --> 00:03:45,725
At first, you were strange and scary to me

50
00:03:46,935 --> 00:03:48,853
But as we spent more time together,

51
00:03:48,853 --> 00:03:51,356
I realized you weren't a bad person

52
00:03:53,066 --> 00:03:54,317
And...

53
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:57,987
I want to hold you close

54
00:04:03,493 --> 00:04:04,827
Minu

55
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:09,374
I'll be by your side from now on

56
00:05:09,976 --> 00:05:10,852
Lucifer

57
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,645
What is all this?

58
00:05:14,314 --> 00:05:17,317
What do you mean? It's breakfast

59
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,862
Oh, come on

60
00:05:55,396 --> 00:05:56,689
Ah...

61
00:05:56,773 --> 00:05:57,899
This is so good

62
00:05:58,274 --> 00:05:58,816
Right?

63
00:05:58,983 --> 00:05:59,734
Tasty, isn't it?

64
00:06:00,109 --> 00:06:02,111
I told you I can cook

65
00:06:02,445 --> 00:06:03,988
What do you want to eat next time?

66
00:06:04,864 --> 00:06:05,448
Huh?

67
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,116
You're going to make more?

68
00:06:08,618 --> 00:06:10,119
If it's something you want,

69
00:06:10,411 --> 00:06:11,746
I'll put in the effort

70
00:06:12,497 --> 00:06:13,456
Oh

71
00:06:15,583 --> 00:06:15,917
Oh!

72
00:06:16,667 --> 00:06:18,544
Isn't it time for you to drink blood?

73
00:06:18,878 --> 00:06:19,587
I'll go get it

74
00:06:20,004 --> 00:06:21,506
I already had some

75
00:06:21,798 --> 00:06:23,216
Come on, just tell me

76
00:06:23,424 --> 00:06:24,842
What do you want to eat next time?

77
00:06:28,388 --> 00:06:30,014
Ah, I'm pretty full now

78
00:06:30,848 --> 00:06:32,266
Should we go out for a walk?

79
00:06:32,475 --> 00:06:33,434
Don't change the subject

80
00:06:33,434 --> 00:06:35,019
How can you get full from this?

81
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,854
No, I really ate a lot

82
00:06:37,939 --> 00:06:38,856
The weather's nice out

83
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:40,233
Let's go to the park

84
00:06:40,233 --> 00:06:41,692
That place we went last time was really nice

85
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:42,860
It's cold outside

86
00:06:43,152 --> 00:06:44,862
No it's not

87
00:06:52,662 --> 00:06:53,788
Ugh, this is boring

88
00:06:54,414 --> 00:06:55,540
Boring?

89
00:06:55,998 --> 00:06:58,459
You just don't know how to ride it, I'll show you

90
00:06:59,085 --> 00:07:00,837
Here, hold on tight

91
00:07:01,129 --> 00:07:02,839
Hey, stop it!

92
00:07:11,347 --> 00:07:12,849
Huh, what?

93
00:07:13,307 --> 00:07:14,142
Oh, it's nothing

94
00:07:14,475 --> 00:07:15,184
Is it tasty?

95
00:07:15,184 --> 00:07:16,436
No, no

96
00:07:16,727 --> 00:07:17,520
Just let me have one bite

97
00:07:17,603 --> 00:07:18,396
- No

98
00:07:19,147 --> 00:07:20,523
- Come on, just one bite

99
00:07:20,690 --> 00:07:21,315
No

100
00:07:22,483 --> 00:07:23,776
Wow, this is actually so fun

101
00:07:24,402 --> 00:07:25,486
Have you read volume 6?

102
00:07:28,322 --> 00:07:29,407
What?

103
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:32,827
This is my first time reading it

104
00:07:34,036 --> 00:07:34,829
Just smell it

105
00:07:36,998 --> 00:07:38,458
Come on, just hand it to me

106
00:07:38,458 --> 00:07:39,292
I'm serious, no

107
00:07:39,876 --> 00:07:41,586
You're dead to me

108
00:07:41,586 --> 00:07:42,378
Okay, okay

109
00:08:29,842 --> 00:08:31,260
Wasn't that a little rough today?

110
00:08:33,387 --> 00:08:35,431
Let me show you the rough love of a vampire

111
00:08:40,436 --> 00:08:43,189
- We'll see another total lunar eclipse tomorrow night

112
00:08:46,651 --> 00:08:47,902
- Large crowds have gathered

113
00:08:47,902 --> 00:08:50,154
- to witness the lunar eclipse
